{"tid":754583,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"試過邊間嘅港式奶茶最正？","createTime":"2018-07-24T13:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T04:33:41.000Z","uid":128910,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e505602c6b392cb4900ecb0fec3f2bc9633260e4","tid":754583,"uid":128910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:42:19.000Z","msg":"有幾個外國朋友黎左香港旅行 有冇巴絲有好介紹？<br />\n<br />\n唔想帶佢地飲貢茶或者宜家好興嘅奶蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  平時自己都係求其揾間茶餐廳 都想試下好少少嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ff439a886e95904c84a4d503d6691bcc650954","tid":754583,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:45:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://etw.nextdigital.com.hk/article/3_58403758\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fetw.nextdigital.com.hk%2Farticle%2F3_58403758&d=fc7yIvJIluIa%2FFMUpegtYZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=4821ddbf\" target=\"_blank\">https://etw.nextdigital.com.hk/article/3_58403758</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭記士多這名字近年突然走紅，原因是士多老闆賣的奶茶夠貴，$68一杯。為何賣這麼貴﹖因為除了喝奶茶，還可以看奶show。老闆會推出一部專為製作奶茶的餐車，從舀、秤、撒茶葉，到注入熱水，把熱水染成茶，將茶注入加了淡奶的茶碗，每個沖茶細節都活生生展現在你眼前。老闆還會教你品嘗奶茶的方法，就是一吞二含三飲。用心地喝，的確能喝到那柔滑如絲的口感，還有奶甜茶甘的味道。呷茶後，口腔還能感受到茶味的餘韻。"},{"pid":"d9443b9052fbdaf9af3c83659dce26993d81f556","tid":754583,"uid":128910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46ff439a886e95904c84a4d503d6691bcc650954","tid":754583,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:45:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://etw.nextdigital.com.hk/article/3_58403758\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fetw.nextdigital.com.hk%2Farticle%2F3_58403758&d=fc7yIvJIluIa%2FFMUpegtYZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=4821ddbf\" target=\"_blank\">https://etw.nextdigital.com.hk/article/3_58403758</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭記士多這名字近年突然走紅，原因是士多老闆賣的奶茶夠貴，$68一杯。為何賣這麼貴﹖因為除了喝奶茶，還可以看奶show。老闆會推出一部專為製作奶茶的餐車，從舀、秤、撒茶葉，到注入熱水，把熱水染成茶，將茶注入加了淡奶的茶碗，每個沖茶細節都活生生展現在你眼前。老闆還會教你品嘗奶茶的方法，就是一吞二含三飲。用心地喝，的確能喝到那柔滑如絲的口感，還有奶甜茶甘的味道。呷茶後，口腔還能感受到茶味的餘韻。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:48:56.000Z","msg":"巴打有冇自己試過？"},{"pid":"d3fc96f8fb534f7273db517dd2943393d95b173b","tid":754583,"uid":125213,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:54:40.000Z","msg":"一定係M記港式奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406a803da7266e18d1a2a6e8574ce716eaac603c","tid":754583,"uid":162567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46ff439a886e95904c84a4d503d6691bcc650954","tid":754583,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:45:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://etw.nextdigital.com.hk/article/3_58403758\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fetw.nextdigital.com.hk%2Farticle%2F3_58403758&d=fc7yIvJIluIa%2FFMUpegtYZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=4821ddbf\" target=\"_blank\">https://etw.nextdigital.com.hk/article/3_58403758</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭記士多這名字近年突然走紅，原因是士多老闆賣的奶茶夠貴，$68一杯。為何賣這麼貴﹖因為除了喝奶茶，還可以看奶show。老闆會推出一部專為製作奶茶的餐車，從舀、秤、撒茶葉，到注入熱水，把熱水染成茶，將茶注入加了淡奶的茶碗，每個沖茶細節都活生生展現在你眼前。老闆還會教你品嘗奶茶的方法，就是一吞二含三飲。用心地喝，的確能喝到那柔滑如絲的口感，還有奶甜茶甘的味道。呷茶後，口腔還能感受到茶味的餘韻。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T14:44:16.000Z","msg":"ON9"},{"pid":"8ce405f6622d2d630698e251ef18bac4302ed0c1","tid":754583,"uid":5112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T15:11:05.000Z","msg":"旺角康年，凍奶茶小甜，仲有菠蘿油<br />\n<br />\n好飲好食過咩金華好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db91ba53424b98ee7cee500e0b7fb89f8fe5b351","tid":754583,"uid":58165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T00:23:20.000Z","msg":"譚仔"},{"pid":"77698fbb2cd9c5d7a2800b25ef68d7ddcdaf68c6","tid":754583,"uid":95118,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T00:24:43.000Z","msg":"熱就大家樂，凍就太興"},{"pid":"d2445be1a041850b91ddf7a90c83ff1a83b0dd19","tid":754583,"uid":27234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T00:24:46.000Z","msg":"澳牛<br />\n叫茶走"},{"pid":"fcef998f69af4c1eaf3a222aaee0a9ee338968bb","tid":754583,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T00:27:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://etw.nextdigital.com.hk/article/3_58403758\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fetw.nextdigital.com.hk%2Farticle%2F3_58403758&d=fc7yIvJIluIa%2FFMUpegtYZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=4821ddbf\" target=\"_blank\">https://etw.nextdigital.com.hk/article/3_58403758</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭記士多這名字近年突然走紅，原因是士多老闆賣的奶茶夠貴，$68一杯。為何賣這麼貴﹖因為除了喝奶茶，還可以看奶show。老闆會推出一部專為製作奶茶的餐車，從舀、秤、撒茶葉，到注入熱水，把熱水染成茶，將茶注入加了淡奶的茶碗，每個沖茶細節都活生生展現在你眼前。老闆還會教你品嘗奶茶的方法，就是<span style=\"color: red;\">一吞二含三飲</span>。用心地喝，的確能喝到那柔滑如絲的口感，還有奶甜茶甘的味道。呷茶後，口腔還能感受到茶味的餘韻。</blockquote><br />\n一乾三濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"326f8d1ff052edc2127405ded9404239d5f092ab","tid":754583,"uid":91398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T00:49:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/milktealogy/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fmilktealogy%2F&d=fc7yIvJIluIa%2FFMUpegtYZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=26af6354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/milktealogy/</a>"},{"pid":"a95728f11dc93fe26ba84164dd92731b9d53ddaf","tid":754583,"uid":159734,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:55:03.000Z","msg":"蘭芳園?"},{"pid":"0de1efd1880171a7d05f0cd2ae20b317cd14b080","tid":754583,"uid":37152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T03:10:08.000Z","msg":"長沙灣新華 鰂魚涌德昌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874efd378b854f78e80c9007516d909379a46cf7","tid":754583,"uid":151324,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T03:11:25.000Z","msg":"華星"},{"pid":"82d4f46656824